## 6. Ace3 Framework

When using Ace3, embed libraries rather than depending on standalone installs.

### 6.1 Basic Ace3 Addon

```lua
local MyAddon = LibStub("AceAddon-3.0"):NewAddon("MyAddon",
    "AceConsole-3.0", "AceEvent-3.0", "AceTimer-3.0")

function MyAddon:OnInitialize()
    -- Fires on ADDON_LOADED. Set up DB, options, etc.
    self.db = LibStub("AceDB-3.0"):New("MyAddonDB", defaults, true)
end

function MyAddon:OnEnable()
    -- Fires on PLAYER_LOGIN. Safe to interact with the world.
    self:RegisterEvent("PLAYER_ENTERING_WORLD")
    self:RegisterChatCommand("myaddon", "SlashHandler")
end

function MyAddon:OnDisable()
    -- Cleanup if the addon is disabled at runtime.
end

function MyAddon:PLAYER_ENTERING_WORLD(event, isLogin, isReload)
    -- AceEvent routes events to methods named after the event.
end

function MyAddon:SlashHandler(input)
    local cmd = self:GetArgs(input)
    -- handle
end
```

### 6.2 AceDB Defaults

```lua
local defaults = {
    profile = {
        enabled = true,
        scale = 1.0,
        position = { x = 0, y = 0 },
    },
    char = {
        -- per-character data
    },
    global = {
        -- account-wide data
    },
}
```

